# Project Commands & Scripts

All commands for the AMS microservices project.

---

## Docker — Start / Stop

```bash
# Start everything (first time or after code changes)
docker compose up --build

# Start without rebuilding
docker compose up -d

# Stop all
docker compose down

# Restart single service
docker compose restart auth-service

# Rebuild single service
docker compose up -d --build auth-service
```

---

## Superuser — Create

```bash
# Auth service (most common — login / user management)
docker exec -it ams_auth python manage.py createsuperuser

# Other services
docker exec -it ams_org          python manage.py createsuperuser
docker exec -it ams_campus       python manage.py createsuperuser
docker exec -it ams_staff        python manage.py createsuperuser
docker exec -it ams_student      python manage.py createsuperuser
docker exec -it ams_attendance   python manage.py createsuperuser
docker exec -it ams_result       python manage.py createsuperuser
docker exec -it ams_fees         python manage.py createsuperuser
docker exec -it ams_timetable    python manage.py createsuperuser
docker exec -it ams_notification python manage.py createsuperuser
docker exec -it ams_support      python manage.py createsuperuser
```

