## Superuser — Fix / Reset

```bash
# Change password
docker exec -it ams_auth python manage.py changepassword <email>

# Give superuser + staff rights via shell
docker exec -it ams_auth python manage.py shell
# Then paste:
from django.contrib.auth import get_user_model
User = get_user_model()
u = User.objects.get(email='your@email.com')
u.is_staff = True
u.is_superuser = True
u.save()
print("Done!")
```

