## Migrations

```bash
# Run migrations (single service)
docker exec -it ams_auth python manage.py migrate

# Make migrations (single service)
docker exec -it ams_auth python manage.py makemigrations

# All services at once
for c in ams_auth ams_org ams_campus ams_staff ams_student ams_attendance ams_result ams_fees ams_timetable ams_notification ams_support; do
  echo "=== $c ===" && docker exec $c python manage.py migrate
done
```

