## Management Commands (Auth service)

```bash
# Seed subscription plans (Basic / Standard / Enterprise)
docker exec -it ams_auth python manage.py seed_plans

# Seed role-based permissions
docker exec -it ams_auth python manage.py seed_permissions

# Create user interactively
docker exec -it ams_auth python manage.py create_user
```

